dbp:caption: Vivian Smith at the 38th Chess Olympiad in Dresden 2008

text: Vivian Joyce Smith (born Vivian Barrowman on 15 September 1951, Auckland, New Zealand), is a chess Woman FIDE Master (WFM). She has represented New Zealand in fifteen Chess Olympiads, and won the New Zealand Women's Chess Championship a record ten times. She is a Member of the New Zealand Order of Merit for her services to chess.
